メソッドの概要
 int getCommits()
          The number of commits which the Ohloh servers have successfully
downloaded from the source control server.
 long getId()
          The unique ID of the Repository.
 Date getLoggedAt()
          The last time the Ohloh servers successfully queried
the source control server for changes.
 String getModuleName()
          For CVS repositories only, this is the module name.
 String getOhlohJobStatus()
          If the most recent attempt by Ohloh to query the source
control server for changes failed or was interrupted,
this value will be `failed`.
 String getPassword()
          An optional password, if one is required
to access the source control server.
 String getType()
          The source control type.
 String getUrl()
          The public URL for the source control server.
 String getUserName()
          An optional username, if one is required
to access the source control server.

getType

String getType()
The source control type. Supported values are: SvnRepository Subversion CvsRepository CVS GitRepository Git HgRepository Mercurial BzrRepository Bazaar SvnSyncRepository Subversion ‘svnsync

戻り値:
the type

getModuleName

String getModuleName()
For CVS repositories only, this is the module name.
For all other repository types, this element is omitted.

戻り値:
the moduleName

getOhlohJobStatus

String getOhlohJobStatus()
If the most recent attempt by Ohloh to query the source
control server for changes failed or was interrupted,
this value will be `failed`. In all other cases it is `success`.

戻り値:
the ohlohJobStatus
